OL,3,C13 year old girl appears in court over
OL,4,Cschool stabbing
OL,6,FThe girl, who cannot be named for
OL,7,Flegal reasons, showed no emotion as
OL,8,Fshe appeared in the dock at Llanelli
OL,9,FMagistrates' Court on Friday.
OL,11,FSpeaking only to confirm her name and
OL,12,Faddress, the teenager, who wore a grey
OL,13,Fjumper, looked small next to the
OL,14,Fcourtroom staff who surrounded her.
OL,16,FShe was charged with three counts of
OL,17,Fattempted murder and possession of a
OL,18,Fbladed article on a school premises,
OL,19,Fand will next appear at Swansea Crown
OL,20,FCourt on May 27.
