OL,3,C13 year old girl appears in court over
OL,4,Cschool stabbing
OL,6,FShe was remanded to a youth detention
OL,7,Faccommodation.
OL,9,FIt comes as a 15-year-old boy was
OL,10,Farrested later on Wednesday after
OL,11,Fpolice received reports about messages
OL,12,Fon social media referring to the
OL,13,Fstabbing.
OL,15,FOne of the teachers injured in the
OL,16,Fattack has been named as Fiona Elias,
OL,17,Fthe head of year seven.
OL,19,FThe second adult is reported to be Liz
OL,20,FHopkin, a special needs teacher.
